# This platform is dependency-free and requires NO environment variables at runtime.
#
# Power Automate HTTP-trigger flow endpoints are managed centrally in
# js/api.js (the FLOW_ENDPOINTS registry) and can be overridden per-flow at
# runtime via the in-app Settings page (stored in browser localStorage).
#
# There is no server, no build step, and no secret injection. See GOVERNANCE.md
# for the governed exceptions covering embedded flow URLs and the OTP gateway.
